R4.0-1.0.0	2022-06-08 Bruce Hill
	R4.0 from EPICS Collab
		Support for new JSON log format
		Support for multiple host:port log clients
	plus:
		Includes a VALUE_2_string function to aid in formatting values in put log.
		Added caPutLogFile iocsh command to support writing the putlog to a file.

R3.7-1.1.0	2022-06-08 Bruce Hill
	Changed VALUE_to_string to VALUE_2_string to avoid conflicts w/ similar function in CA gateway.

R3.7-1.0.0	2020-04-08	Bruce Hill
	SLAC changes for IOC and gateway support:
		Added caPutLogFile iocsh command
		Add VALUE_to_string() to the API.
	R3.7 Fixes:	Andrew Johnson
		Fix memory leak for log messages that can't be queued
		More int64 support, in val_to_string()
		Register an epicsAtExit() routine for shutdown
		Increase log message line length
	R3.6 Fixes: Dirk Zimoch
		Remove 64 bit warnings

R3.5-1.0.0  06-Feb-2017, H. Slepicka (slepicka)
    Applied patch <>/patches/0001-caPutLogFile_and_build_changes
        Add caPutLogFile and tweaks configuration files.

R3.5-0.1.0  03-Feb-2017, H. Slepicka (slepicka)
    First version of caPutLog working with the new Git Workflow.
